{"tid":832201,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"上連登見證人既成長","createTime":"2018-09-22T15:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T00:48:06.000Z","uid":185449,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a67ce8bb26b0be26069170b7c29551f660d431","tid":832201,"uid":185449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"上連登睇咩台原來好真實反映你果刻人生處於咩階段<br />\n<br />\n由高中開始一直睇學術台 當時高登既學術台係可以用知識寶庫黎形容 仲記得果陣好多手足有學術問題就會放上黎問 大家係理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔似得而家中學牛屌小學雞 五十步笑百步既做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   仲有就係感情台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到大學畢業前會留意上班台 成班跪求offer 圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n畢業做左野一排再進一步後就多留意財經台同汽車台 會留意股票，同班巴打圍爐打飛機睇下層樓升幾多同點裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前排多左筆閒錢就上汽車台留意下換咩車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當上面每一樣野都經歷緊/ 經歷過既時候 而家上連登已經只會掃吹水台同埋睇熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  實在唔知人生既重點應該放邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5eec21410248955840e9c739762fa429d30f3f9","tid":832201,"uid":125079,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:39:41.000Z","msg":"再大啲身體差咗, 多病痛<br />\n<br />\n就上健康台問人點醫病 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a25fe46e08e5bcb3b6f4808eab24f59f4a468a6","tid":832201,"uid":44019,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"連登落後過以前高登好多,唉"},{"pid":"d130ffe0de70d6b3145ec7e43db47ed3c75f35c0","tid":832201,"uid":44019,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:01:02.000Z"